name: EVERGREEN EUREKA
briefDescription: EVERGREEN EUREKA has passed another colorful year of activities during 2016-17 on the eve of new millennium, we convey our heartful thanks to all who cooperated with us for fulfillment of our plan and programme. The organization is a got registered group working for the socio-economic development of the weaker section of the people specially for the welfare of the most distressed and depressed women belonging to SCs, STs, Minorities and backward communities. It is a voluntary organization registered in 2007 under the Bihar societies Registration Act, 21, 1860. It is mainly organized and oriented for the welfare of target group belonging to women folk of most distressed communities through promotional, cultural economic and all round development.
